pect班老師同你一齊舉杯大叫飲勝掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3249db1f22131298ffcfac19de450998520ed342","tid":238920,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T13:21:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多時搞手係身不由己<br />\nbtw 樓主唔係讀緊ive咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc759507bc1a2e7bb9aad09283195d4dc60f5a0f","tid":238920,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T13:22:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未考完試喎樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,學生會話早D搞冇咁貴,dse完左"},{"pid":"fe50218bd39de3c058a6ab73e97260b4b17be5f9","tid":238920,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T13:23:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>琴日既謝師宴，終於可以睇清楚E家年輕人既真面目。因為我冇錢買西裝，所以就著上一套快乾運動裝去。一入到酒店，有D人已經在發牢騷，擺明「見高拜，見低踩。」！<br />\n之後我搵人影相，我發覺他們拿起ＤＳＬＲ當傻瓜機拎，分明想亂咁影。<br />\n<br />\n本來我都想唔去，但是又有人話係到搞分化，搞到我非去不可。<br />\n<br />\n我希望大家討論以下問題：<br />\n一‧現今年輕人的崇洋主義是否過重，為甚麼一定要穿西裝才能去，穿快乾運動裝就遭人歧視？<br />\n二‧謝師宴為甚麼一定要在西式酒店搞，而不能在一間較高級中式海鮮酒家搞？</blockquote><br />\n1. 唔係崇洋主義, 而係咩場合著咩衫, 謝師宴冇話一定要西裝, smart casual都得, 甚至唐裝都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2. 高級中式海鮮酒家, 你唔係會expect班老師同你一齊舉杯大叫飲勝掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題係點解大家預設左人人都要西式呢,<br />\n中式=古怪,老土?"},{"pid":"7f9e76aee67114c57ec4031700abc738ed5778ce","tid":238920,"uid":67093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T13:25:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>未考完試喎樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,學生會話早D搞冇咁貴,dse完左</blockquote><br />\neng oral 都未完呀on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/